title: Amy Spills Tea About Bobby’s New York Date + Lunchbox Reads Scripture

description:
Amy “Spills The Tea” about a date Bobby went on while he was in New York this week. Also, Lunchbox reads the scripture he missed reading at his brother-in-law’s wedding because of the flu.
